  20,25,"[Mûsâ (Moses)] said: "
  20,26,""
  20,27,""
  21,1,"Draws near for mankind their reckoning, while they turn away in heedlessness."
  21,2,"Comes not unto them an admonition (a chapter of the Qur’ân) from their Lord as a recent revelation but they listen to it while they play"
  21,3,"With their hearts occupied (with evil things). Those who do wrong, conceal their private counsels, (saying): "